Login package for Nodejs
Morgan: npm install --save morgan

To extract Reaquest body of an incoming request (e.g POST request), we need to install a package called "body-parser"
: npm install --save body-parser

To connect with the database, we need to install a database package called "Mongoose"
:  npm install --save mongoose

TO upload images and other form data e.g texts and files
To be able to read incoming requests which holds form data which is a different content type.
:npm install --save multer
........"Multer is like 'body-parser', able to parse incoming bodies i.e form data bodies
........It is an alternative to body-parser when dealing with bodies cannot be handle by body-parser


To encrypt password
::: npm install bcrypt


To install json web token
:   npm install jsonwebtoken